---

<Layout
  lang={lang}
  title="Encuentros — Work"
  description="Encuentros con seres notables (2022). Sculpture — savanna jasmine branches, eucalyptus, wood carving, clay. Maria Elvira Escallon."
  ogImage={enc01.src}
>


  <ArtworkSchema
    title="Encuentros con seres notables"
    year="2022"
    medium="Sculpture, carved branches"
    description="Sculptures carved from branches that explore the relationship between the human body and the vegetal."
    url="https://sebastianoguerae.github.io/maria-elvira-escallon/en/works/encuentros-con-seres-notables/"
  />

  <article class="work-page">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="work-page__header">
        <p class="label">Work / 011</p>
        <h1>{title}</h1>
        <p class="work-page__meta">2022 &nbsp;/&nbsp; Sculpture — savanna jasmine branches, eucalyptus, wood carving, clay &nbsp;/&nbsp; Variable dimensions</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Gallery -->
      <div class="work-page__gallery">
        <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">ENCUENTROS</h3>
        <Image src={enc01} alt="Encuentros — Sculpture on branch, emerging figure" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={enc02} alt="Encuentros — Wood carving on natural branch" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={enc07} alt="Encuentros — Detail of sculptural intervention" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={enc08} alt="Encuentros — Human form in tree branch" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />

        <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">ENCUENTROS CON SERES NOTABLES</h3>
        <Image src={seres01} alt="Encuentros con seres notables — Sculpture carved on branch" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={seres03} alt="Encuentros con seres notables — Intervened vegetal body" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={seres04} alt="Encuentros con seres notables — Detail of wood carving" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={seres05} alt="Encuentros con seres notables — Carved organic form" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={seres06} alt="Encuentros con seres notables — Branch with sculptural figure" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={seres10} alt="Encuentros con seres notables — Ensemble view" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />

        <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">MESA DE TRABAJO</h3>
        <Image src={mesa01} alt="Mesa de trabajo — General view of the workspace" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa15} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Tools and materials" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa16} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Carving process" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa17} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Branches in preparation" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa18} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Detail of creative process" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa19} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Pieces in development" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa20} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Sculptural material" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa21} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Carving fragments" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa22} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Work elements" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa23} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Studio view" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa24} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Detail of tools" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa25} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Finished pieces" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa26} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Process record" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={mesa27} alt="Mesa de trabajo — Final view of the space" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />

        <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">ARBOREA</h3>
        <Image src={arborea08} alt="Arborea — Intervened arboreal sculpture" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={arborea09} alt="Arborea — Detail of intervention on tree" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />

        <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">ENCUENTROS CERCANOS</h3>
        <Image src={cercanos12} alt="Encuentros cercanos — Carved figure in close-up" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={cercanos13} alt="Encuentros cercanos — Detail of sculptural form" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
        <Image src={cercanos14} alt="Encuentros cercanos — Close view of carving" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />

        <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">LAS CAMINANTES</h3>
        <Image src={caminantes11} alt="Las caminantes — Walking figure carved in branch" loading="lazy" widths={[480, 900, 1400]} sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 1200px" />
      </div>

      <!-- Video -->
      <div class="work-page__video">
        <div class="work-page__video-header">
          <h3>VIDEO</h3>
          <span class="label">Encuentros</span>
        </div>
        <video controls preload="metadata">
          <source src="/maria-elvira-escallon/video/encuentros-web.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
      </div>

      <!-- Text + Technical sheet -->
      <div class="work-page__body">
        <div class="work-page__text">

          <p class="curatorial">
            With these pieces, we bring into consideration the characteristics that bring us closer to vegetal beings, instead of emphasizing what differentiates us from other species and families, as has been done for centuries. The project also suggests a modified image of the human, whose anatomical structure is associated with and dialogues with that of vegetal beings.
          </p>

          <p class="curatorial" style="margin-top: var(--s2);">
            Encuentros -1 In this set of sculptural pieces, branches of different botanical species meet and merge into one another, giving rise to a continuum. Thus a branch of encenillo — a native species of the Andean sub-paramo — merges with a branch of eucalyptus, a species from Japan. The series ends with the piece La superneurona, made in France, where the crown of a pine from America is coupled with a European White Chestnut.
          </p>

          <p class="curatorial" style="margin-top: var(--s2);">
            Encuentros con Seres Notables. The piece simultaneously presents three images that the public can immediately recognize: the image of Michelangelo's painting The Creation of Adam, the image of human arm and hand bones, and branches of two varieties of trees slightly intervened. It evokes associations with concepts of creation, life, death, as well as pacts, alliances, and transmissions of knowledge. It presents fusions between distant species and even between different kingdoms.
          </p>

          <p class="curatorial" style="margin-top: var(--s2);">
            In the video Mesa de trabajo, which is part of this series, a replica of the face of the Venus sculpture is broken and reduced to dust with the help of various domestic implements. This dust is then mixed with water to model a figure that combines human and vegetal anatomy.
          </p>

        </div>

        <aside class="work-page__ficha">
          <h4>TECHNICAL SHEET</h4>
          <div class="ficha">
            <strong>Encuentros</strong><br>
            2017–2022<br><br>
            Sculpture — savanna jasmine branches, eucalyptus, wood carving, clay.<br><br>
            Variable dimensions.
          </div>

          <h4 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">HOW TO CITE</h4>
          <div class="ficha" style="font-size: 0.65rem;">
            Escallon, M.E. (2017–2022). “Encuentros con seres notables”.
            Sculpture. Available at:
            sebastianoguerae.github.io/maria-elvira-escallon/en/works/encuentros-con-seres-notables/
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

  </article>

</Layout>
